modules.description: Provides functions for parsing and serializing WAMP protocol messages, including handling tuples, lists, and binary data. Implements message encoding and decoding for events, calls, and subscriptions. Used to process real-time communication data in distributed systems.

Handles conversion between WAMP messages and JSON using Yojson, supporting parsing and serialization. Operates on WAMP message types, URI references, and JSON dictionaries. Used to construct and process WAMP 'hello' and 'subscribe' messages with custom options and request IDs.
